Payload

Represents the payload contained within a log entry.

  • Value

    The payload contains an arbitrary value, or nil.

    Declaration

    Swift

    case Value(Any?)
  • Message

    The payload contains a text message.

    Declaration

    Swift

    case Message(String)
  • Trace

    The log entry is a trace call and contains no explicit payload.

    Declaration

    Swift

    case Trace
